    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of the wide-body 996.2. This specimen features the M96 3.6L flat-six, delivering 315 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and an advanced all-wheel-drive system. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The chassis retains its factory rigidity, complemented by 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for superior thermal management. Finished in pristine Lapis Blue Metallic over a supple Graphite Grey leather interior, this C4S exhibits zero paint aeration or bolster wear. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
