      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather seats are firm with no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronics, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records, always performed at authorized intervals. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfect example of this model, complete with both keys, original window sticker, and a custom car cover.",
